str2: Not, lest. A primary particle of qualified negation; not, lest; also (whereas ou expects an affirmative one) whether.

str2: To make drunk; pass: I become drunk. A prolonged form of methuo; to intoxicate.

str2: I am, exist. The first person singular present indicative; a prolonged form of a primary and defective verb; I exist.
Wantonness, profligacy, wastefulness. From a compound of a and a presumed derivative of sozo; properly, unsavedness, i.e. profligacy.
But, except, however. Neuter plural of allos; properly, other things, i.e. contrariwise.

str2: From pleres; to make replete, i.e. to cram, level up, or to furnish, satisfy, execute, finish, verify, etc.
In, on, among. A primary preposition denoting position, and instrumentality, i.e. A relation of rest; 'in, ' at, on, by, etc.
